arn.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the EKS add-on.

created_at.description: Date and time in RFC3339 format that the EKS add-on was created.

id.description: EKS Cluster name and EKS Addon name separated by a colon (:).

modified_at.description: Date and time in RFC3339 format that the EKS add-on was updated.
